section.section:
"Health insurer" includes:
a health maintenance organization operating under a certificate of authority issued by the Commissioner under Title 19, Subtitle 7 of the Health - General Article;
a nonprofit health service plan operating under Title 14, Subtitle 1 of this article;
a dental plan operating under Title 14, Subtitle 4 of this article; and
a provider-sponsored organization operating under Title 19, Subtitle 7A of the Health - General Article.

"Insurer" includes:
a health maintenance organization operating under a certificate of authority issued by the Commissioner under Title 19, Subtitle 7 of the Health - General Article;
a nonprofit health service plan operating under Title 14, Subtitle 1 of this article;
a dental plan operating under Title 14, Subtitle 4 of this article; and
a provider-sponsored organization operating under Title 19, Subtitle 7A of the Health - General Article.

"Property and casualty insurer" does not include:
a health maintenance organization operating under a certificate of authority issued by the Commissioner under Title 19, Subtitle 7 of the Health - General Article;
a nonprofit health service plan operating under Title 14, Subtitle 1 of this article;
a dental plan operating under Title 14, Subtitle 4 of this article;
a provider-sponsored organization operating under Title 19, Subtitle 7A of the Health - General Article; or
a managed care organization operating under Title 15, Subtitle 1 of the Health - General Article.

text.section:
"RBC level" means an insurer's company action level RBC, regulatory action level RBC, authorized control level RBC, or mandatory control level RBC if:
"company action level RBC" means the product of 2.0 and the authorized control level RBC;
"regulatory action level RBC" means the product of 1.5 and the authorized control level RBC;
"authorized control level RBC" means the number determined under the risk based capital formula in accordance with the RBC instructions; or
"mandatory control level RBC" means the product of .70 and the authorized control level RBC.
